{"tid":2229493,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己有鼻咽癌，跪求意見","createTime":"2020-10-04T12:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:07:46.000Z","uid":135262,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"67021f12674c35c7c5ce7f14565a60c059fff875","tid":2229493,"uid":135262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"文有少少長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，主要想問邊到做檢查同埋收費幾多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月左右開始久唔久(大概每一兩日)朝早起身抹鼻哥會有血，當時以為開得冷氣多先流鼻血，所以冇點理到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月開始就慢慢冇再流鼻血，但9月中開始無啦啦耳仔有種好似塞住左嘅感覺。我以為過幾日會好返，結果一個禮拜後都未好返，就去睇耳鼻喉醫生。<br />\n<br />\n去到醫生幫我攞燈照下耳仔照下鼻，話冇咩問題，就話我係耳咽管塞住，幫我夾左粒耳屎出黎，同埋開幾日藥比我食。<br />\n<br />\n我開始食藥之後嗰段日子耳仔的確冇咁塞，但係係我食最後一日藥嗰晚，耳仔突然有耳鳴，唔確定邊一邊。上網睇過d病徵，懷疑自己可能有鼻咽癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n想問下我係咪應該盡快去檢查，同埋應該去邊度做檢查、大概收費有幾貴，感激不盡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我得二十歲仔，但都有d怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bc53d11736ffbc9d75c4d2f1c13eaeb1559eb0","tid":2229493,"uid":223959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"有冇睇耳鼻喉專科？"},{"pid":"004e20119796b3768682833ddf8705a5a7e28b3b","tid":2229493,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddbc4371c587e264fa442865d7650676784d8e32","tid":2229493,"uid":327934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"有買保險搵agent問個睇醫生流程<br />\n無街睇街診請醫生幫你寫紙"},{"pid":"5f2e4ec7a6a25c6766ef4b28c0a6a5ed25b16c05","tid":2229493,"uid":135262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16bc53d11736ffbc9d75c4d2f1c13eaeb1559eb0","tid":2229493,"uid":223959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"有冇睇耳鼻喉專科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"上個月有睇，醫生淨係話我耳咽管鼻塞，比左四日藥我食only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2568c5fef57a1b24d83ba05cf49d9ea3b6fb9df3","tid":2229493,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"冇事，我話既"},{"pid":"99b5d2180d34ab799bfe96c14a216eb11d8a5118","tid":2229493,"uid":135262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ddbc4371c587e264fa442865d7650676784d8e32","tid":2229493,"uid":327934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"有買保險搵agent問個睇醫生流程<br />\n無街睇街診請醫生幫你寫紙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:37:38.000Z","msg":"唔肯定屋企買左咩保險同有咩流程，返去問一問先，唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e9d0685489be8fb306129497a4b636ac99fa4a","tid":2229493,"uid":223959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f2e4ec7a6a25c6766ef4b28c0a6a5ed25b16c05","tid":2229493,"uid":135262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16bc53d11736ffbc9d75c4d2f1c13eaeb1559eb0","tid":2229493,"uid":223959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"有冇睇耳鼻喉專科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"上個月有睇，醫生淨係話我耳咽管鼻塞，比左四日藥我食only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"耳鼻喉科有得照內規鏡，好似2000幾蚊，佢噴啲麻醉藥你個鼻度，再塞支鏡入去，（少少唔舒服），見到有野/疑似要採樣化驗（麻醉唔痛但留勁多血）"},{"pid":"681e1cf219b19c73bf6ef64859a41e40